data.description: **New Price Adjustment** Are you looking for a ranch home that is ''simply incredible'' and offers beautiful lake and mountain views? The 3 bedroom 2 bath open floor plan with 9 ft. ceilings features an amazing kitchen with an abundance of cabinetry, granite countertops, and an island with seating and storage.  All the kitchen appliances are included with purchase as well as the washer and dryer. The current owner has spent thousands on making this home efficient with new heat and air system. The huge family room features build-ins and a stacked stone wood burning fireplace for those cold winter nights. The master en-suite has tons of space to fit those large pieces of furniture and the master bath boasts a walk-in shower, soaking tub, double sinks and large walk-in closet. Don't miss the built in safe behind the wood shelves in the master closet!  The back yard is described as your own little Oasis with covered sitting area. Enjoy the amazing lake and mountain views from your above ground swimming pool with new pool pump. A great spot to entertain your friends and family or just a peaceful retreat. Take note of the professionally landscaped fenced back yard and shade trees. The shed which is only a few years old and carport also convey with purchase. If you have a lot of things or''stuff'', this is the place for you! Private boat dock for Dogwood Shores Residents.
